Webex App | Make someone a team moderator
If you're a team moderator in Webex App, you can select other people to be a moderator, too. Then they'll be able to make the same changes to the team as you, like adding or removing people or changing the team info.
Windows
Mac
iPhone and iPad, Android
Web
If you're a team moderator, you can add someone else as a moderator, which also adds them to the team.
Go to your Teams and choose the team. Select Add Team Moderator and enter the person's name.

  You can also right-click on someone in the Team moderators list to remove them as a moderator.